. After demonstrating how combinations of the numerous and multiform judgment devices can be used to identify different market models, Karpik applies his analytical tools to the functioning of a large number of actual markets, including fine wines, movies, luxury goods, pop music, and legal services.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 0aEconomicsxSociological aspects. 0aProduct differentiation. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / Theory.2bisacsh1 aScott, Nora.40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781400835218zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781400835218423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781400835218/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK